<div class="media-wrapper"><img src="https://cdn.macstories.net/dj-with-apple-music-1742921981582.jpg" alt="Source: Apple."><p class="image-caption">Source: Apple.</p></div>
<p id="p2">Apple has announced a partnership with DJ software and hardware platforms to integrate Apple Music&rsquo;s catalog into their offerings.</p>
<p id="p3">The new program, called <a href="https://music.apple.com/curator/dj-with-apple-music/1798261090" rel="noopener noreferrer">DJ with Apple Music</a>, expands on an integration that was already in place for <a href="https://www.algoriddim.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Algoriddim</a>&rsquo;s djay Pro app adding <a href="https://alphatheta.com/en/" rel="noopener noreferrer">AlphaTheta</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://serato.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Serato</a>, and inMusic&rsquo;s&nbsp;<a href="https://enginedj.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Engine DJ,</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.denondj.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Denon DJ</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://www.numark.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Numark</a>, and&nbsp;<a href="https://www.rane.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">RANE DJ</a>.</p>
<p id="p4">In an emailed press release, Apple Music&rsquo;s Stephen Campbell, Global Head of Dance, Electronic &amp; DJ Mixes said:</p>
<blockquote id="blockquote5"><p>
  Apple Music is committed to supporting DJs. With this latest integration, we&rsquo;re taking that commitment even further&mdash;seamlessly connecting Apple Music with the industry&rsquo;s leading DJ software and hardware. This innovation brings the full power of Apple Music into the creative workflow, making it easier than ever for DJs to access, play, and discover music in real time.
</p></blockquote>
<p id="p6">Starting today, you can visit a dedicated DJ with Apple Music in the Music app on all platforms. There, you&rsquo;ll find curated playlists picked for DJs by the Apple Music editorial team and links to pages dedicated to each of the participants in the program.</p>
<p id="p7">To check out the available playlists and other materials you can follow this <a href="https://music.apple.com/curator/dj-with-apple-music/1798261090" rel="noopener noreferrer">link</a>.</p>
